.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, photographer, accountant, police-officer, social-worker
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, ice-hockey, cricket, golf
5 different games are played: snooker, canasta, billiard, backgammon, poker
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
There 5 different types of food: lettuce, pineapple, peas, radish, orange

1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the project-manager
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating lettuce
3. the person drinking coffee is the photographer
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking tea
5. the photographer is to the right of the accountant
6. the person playing snooker is the person eating orange
7. the person playing canasta is the police-officer
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left
10. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple
11. the person playing canasta is to the left or right of the person eating radish
12. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person who's sport is golf is the person playing poker
14. the person who's sport is cricket is to the left or right of the social-worker

